{"tid":1281853,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"男子爬出海富中心行人天橋 議員孖市民合力救返","createTime":"2019-07-03T11:44:46.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-03T11:57:11.000Z","uid":103156,"like":9,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"14af548fcb61b7f2d30bee34661b6f5aafbb26cd","tid":1281853,"uid":103156,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-03T11:44:46.000Z","msg":"男子爬出海富中心行人天橋 議員孖市民合力救返<br />\n <a href=\"http://s.nextmedia.com/realtime/a.php?i=20190703&amp;s=10829391&amp;a=59785258\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fs.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fa.php%3Fi%3D20190703%26s%3D10829391%26a%3D59785258&d=Cxq6fU51OcuVLB8gp8NaV5Khd8YmQljH21R%2F5cbT5WU%3D&h=662bd87c\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fs.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fa.php%3Fi%3D20190703%26s%3D10829391%26a%3D59785258&h=dadd5a01\" target=\"_blank\">http://s.nextmedia.com/realtime/a.php?i=20190703&amp;s=10829391&amp;a=59785258</a><br />\n<br />\n下午4時許，一名30多歲男子爬出金鐘夏愨道的海富中心行人天橋圍欄，途人見狀立即大喝，並衝上前將他拉回安全位置，男子事後由救護車送院檢查，警方正調查事件原因。<br />\n<br />\n據悉，多名網民今晨收到消息，指有人欲在金鐘一帶輕生，遂於海富中心一帶巡邏，意圖阻止事件發生。至下午4時許，多人發現一名男子爬出海富中心行人天橋的圍欄，於是大喝阻止，當時立法會議員許智峯及張超雄亦在現場，得悉消息後趕至，並聯同途人合力將他拉回橋上。"},{"pid":"b1d5d7e6c1e3752d7887951c723fabfb3dc39dce","tid":1281853,"uid":103156,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-03T11:46:26.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/o1ULWRK.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fo1ULWRK.png&h=23943ffd&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/hkhxBRM.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FhkhxBRM.png&h=60518835&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"4d66208457b92d15b435803ede942033cba2a518","tid":1281853,"uid":221265,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"14af548fcb61b7f2d30bee34661b6f5aafbb26cd","tid":1281853,"uid":103156,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-03T11:44:46.000Z","msg":"男子爬出海富中心行人天橋 議員孖市民合力救返<br />\n <a href=\"http://s.next